<span id="freeTextContainer17348394513212745451">Some of the writing was quite good, so I can&apos;t give it a poor rating. But this book really needed an editor. I prefer a more tightly structured narrative. This one was constantly breaking away to talk about people and events that had nothing to do with the plot or the main characters. They might have made for good anecdotes, but they didn&apos;t belong in the novel. Plus, I despised the ending. I was very disappointed.</span>
  <span id="freeText17348394513212745451" style="display:none">Some of the writing was quite good, so I can't give it a poor rating. But this book really needed an editor. I prefer a more tightly structured narrative. This one was constantly breaking away to talk about people and events that had nothing to do with the plot or the main characters. They might have made for good anecdotes, but they didn't belong in the novel. Plus, I despised the ending. I was very disappointed.</span>
